Desc.LocalizedString:
Transforms into multiple ink doppelgangers and becomes invincible for a short duration, dealing damage equal to <shuzhi>{0}%</> of ATK to nearby targets. Then gathers the ink to unleash an ink attack, drawing in nearby targets and dealing damage up to <shuzhi>{1}%</> of ATK to them. Cooldown: <shuzhi>30</>s.
 Gathers <shuzhi>Calligraphy Characters</> on the field with In All Directions and unleashes Flaming Bird, dealing damage equal to (number of Summons and Calligraphy Characters, up to <shuzhi>8</>) × <shuzhi>{2}%</> of ATK to nearby targets. Activates <shuzhi>Pinnacle</>, increasing Speed by <shuzhi>{3}%</> for <shuzhi>30</>s.
 <shuzhi>Pinnacle</> grants different effects based on the types and number of <shuzhi>Calligraphy Characters</> gathered:
 Increases Shatter by <shuzhi>{4}%</> when there are <shuzhi>2</> characters "携" (Xié);
 Reduces the cooldown of In All Directions by <shuzhi>3</>s when there are <shuzhi>2</> characters "技" (Jì);
 Grants <shuzhi>{5}</> Dodge attempts when there are <shuzhi>2</> characters "闪" (Shǎn);
 Grants <shuzhi>{6}%</> Damage Reduction while using Normal Attacks when there are <shuzhi>2</> characters "攻" (Gōng);

 <shuzhi>Passive: Calligraphy Characters</>
 Using Discharge, Skills, Dodge, or Normal Attack with any weapons drops corresponding <shuzhi>Calligraphy Characters</>.
 <shuzhi>Discharge</>: Using <shuzhi>1</> Discharge drops <shuzhi>1</> character "携" (Xié). Up to <shuzhi>2</> Discharge characters can exist at a time.
 <shuzhi>Skill</>: Using <shuzhi>1</> Skill drops <shuzhi>1</> character "技" (Jì). Up to <shuzhi>2</> Skill characters can exist at a time.
 <shuzhi>Dodge</>: Using <shuzhi>2</> Dodges drops <shuzhi>1</> character "闪" (Shǎn). Up to <shuzhi>2</> Dodge characters can exist at a time.
 <shuzhi>Attack</>: Using <shuzhi>4</> Normal Attacks drops <shuzhi>1</> character "攻" (Gōng). Up to <shuzhi>2</> Attack characters can exist at a time.

While on the ground, use normal attack to launch five consecutive strikes.
 First strike: Deals damage equal to <shuzhi>{0}%</> of ATK to the target and knocks them back;
 Second strike: Deals damage equal to <shuzhi>{2}%</> of ATK to the target and knocks them back;
 Third strike: Deals damage equal to <shuzhi>{4}%</> of ATK to the target and knocks them back;
 Fourth strike: Deals damage up to <shuzhi>{6}%</> of ATK to the target and knocks them back;
 Fifth strike: Deals damage equal to <shuzhi>{8}%</> of ATK to the target and knocks them up.

 Grants a brief Resistance and Hyperbody boost upon hitting a target with a Normal or Dodge Attack (scales with character level) and further increases Physical Resistance.
 Hold Normal Attack after triggering <shuzhi>Brandishing Spear: Forming Shadow</> to activate <shuzhi>Reverent Spear: Raging Wave</>.

